  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a skillet, sauté garlic and onion until translucent.",
    "Add fennel sausage to the skillet and cook for about 5 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Mix in fresh thyme, chicken stock, red wine vinegar, and olive oil. Bring to a simmer.",
    "Transfer mixture to an oven-safe dish. Top with grated pecorino romano cheese.",
    "Bake for 15-20 minutes or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Serve immediately."
